Description: Start condition for the start of a sequence via asignal input.0 / Rising Edge: Rising edge1 / Falling Edge: Falling edge2 / 1-level: 1 level3 / 0-level: 0 levelThe start condition defines the way the startrequest is to be processed. This setting is used forthe first start after activation of the operatingmode.Modified settings become active the next time themotor moves.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 302D:8hModbus 11536Profibus 11536CIP 145.1.8ModbusTCP 11536EtherCAT 302D:8hPROFINET 11536
